      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Oct 2021 13:57:33 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://ejhu.com/posts/unable-to-turn-on-windows-send-optional-data-diagnostics/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;问题 
    &lt;div id=&#34;%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
